Rinse the @hibiscus flowers(bissap){2%cups}. 

Bring the @hibiscus flowers(bissap) and @water{2.5%l} to a boil until the water is fully colored. 

Let it cool and then remove the @hibiscus flowers(bissap) (bissap) from the cooking juice. 

Add the @sugar{100%g}, @vanilla sugar{2%tbsp}, @nutmeg{1%pinch}, and @orange water blossom{2%tbsp} to this juice and mix.

Chill for ~{5%hours} and serve very cold.